comments:
Wassim, PDEState should actually check the return value of 
State#updateBundle.  If it returns false then you should call 
State#addBundle.  The following code ...

	if (bundleId == -1)
		fState.addBundle(descriptor);
	else
		fState.updateBundle(descriptor);

Can be replaced by this ...

	if (!fState.updateBundle(descriptor))
		fState.addBundle(descriptor);
